Package com.poesys.db.dto

Interface Summary
IDbDto Base interface for the database Data Transfer Objects (DTOs).
IDtoCache<T extends IDbDto> An interface for a cache of data transfer objects (DTOs); you can cache a DTO, get a DTO from the cache using its primary key, remove a DTO from the cache using its primary key, or clear the entire cache.
IObserver The DTO observer provides the observer part of an Observer design pattern interface for DTO objects.
ISet A Strategy-pattern interface for strategies that set data members of a Data Transfer Object.
ISubject The DTO subject provides the subject part of the Observer design pattern interface for DTO objects.
IValidate A Strategy-pattern interface for strategies that validate data members of a Data Transfer Object.
 

Class Summary
AbstractBatchDeleteSetter<T extends IDbDto> An abstract implementation of the ISet interface for a Strategy-pattern class that deletes a collection of DTOs as part of a more comprehensive transaction, taking in a connection and not closing it.

AbstractDeleteSetter<T extends IDbDto> An abstract implementation of the ISet interface for a Strategy-pattern class that deletes a single DTO as part of a more comprehensive transaction, taking in a connection and not closing it.
AbstractDto An abstract implementation of the IDbDto interface for data transfer objects.
AbstractInsertSetter<T extends IDbDto> An abstract implementation of the ISet interface for a Strategy-pattern class that inserts a single DTO as part of a more comprehensive transaction, taking in a connection and not closing it.
AbstractLazyListSetter<T extends IDbDto,P extends IDbDto,C extends Collection<T>> An abstract implementation of the ISet interface for a Strategy-pattern class that sets a list element of a data transfer object as a lazy-loading operation, taking in a connection and closing it.
AbstractLazyLoadingDtoProxy The AbstractLazyLoadingDtoProxy is a Proxy-pattern class that abstracts the shared services required to proxy a data transfer object (DTO) to add lazy-loading services to its members.
AbstractLazyObjectSetter<T extends IDbDto> An abstract implementation of the ISet interface for a Strategy-pattern class that sets an object within a data transfer object as a lazy-loading operation, taking in a connection and closing it.
AbstractListReadSetter<T extends IDbDto> An abstract implementation of the ISet interface for a Strategy-pattern class that sets a list element of a data transfer object as part of a de-serialization read-object process.

AbstractObjectSetter<T extends IDbDto> An abstract implementation of the ISet interface for a Strategy-pattern class that sets an object element of a data transfer object as part of a more comprehensive transaction, taking in a connection and not closing it.
AbstractProcessNestedObject<T extends IDbDto> An abstract implementation of the ISet interface that contains the logic for processing a single DTO, determining which operation it requires.
AbstractProcessNestedObjects<T extends IDbDto,C extends Collection<T>> An abstract implementation of the ISet interface that contains the logic for looping over a set of DTOs, determining which operation to take for each.
AbstractSetter<T extends IDbDto> An abstract class that centralizes things for all setters.
AbstractUpdateSetter<T extends IDbDto> An abstract implementation of the ISet interface for a Strategy-pattern class that updates a single DTO as part of a more comprehensive transaction, taking in a connection and not closing it.
DtoCache<T extends IDbDto> The DtoCache provides a concurrent map cache for the objects of the concrete class.
DtoCacheWithMessaging<T extends IDbDto> Adds messaging to the methods in the superclass DtoCache.
DtoMemcached<T extends IDbDto> The DtoMemcached class implements a caching scheme using the open source memcached distributed caching system.
HasPrimaryKey<T extends IDbDto> Implements a generic validator for checking that a Data Transfer Object (DTO) has a primary key.
 

Enum Summary
IDbDto.Status Enumerated type with the four possible states of the object
 

Exception Summary
DtoStatusException An exception that indicates that a Data Transfer Object (DTO) violates a constraint.
